{
  "stem": "10768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was such an Orthodox town, even if there were a high school, my parents would not allow me to go on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in a high school, it was compulsory to go on a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I studied privately in my spare time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And beginning in December 1939, I decided to leave the family in Oswiecim and go to my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents live in Lesko, which was at the River San but just on the eastern bank of the River San.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our town was on the boundary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the western side were the Germans, and on the eastern side, Lesko was situated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I decided to go home, I took along my personal belonging.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also, I had some money-- not too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But since I was working and, and I was thrifty, I had maybe 200 or 300 zloty, which was not too much money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time were already rumors that on the Russian side items are very expensive, like watches, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know what [NON-ENGLISH] is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A cigarette lighter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cigarette lighter-- the little stones that you put in cigarette lighter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were small items.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I spent 200 or 300 zloty, and I bought these items, which are two small packages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took off home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The trains were already running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This part of Poland was really not, not destroyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps Warsaw was destroyed, and I was never in Warsaw at this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this part-- the trains were not running normally but slowly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took me until I came to a town, Sanok.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sanok was on, on the western part of the River San.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came there from, from our, from the train, I had to take like a little-- with a horse and buggy to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
